<h3>Sick Room Facility:</h3>

Sick room with minimal support is available in the health center that can be used by those who have been advised isolation by the doctor. 
</p>
<p align="justify">
<h3>Emergency:</h3>

<b>(1) Institute Ambulance:</b> During non-office hours, inform the hostel/nearest security and he/she will request for the Institute ambulance. During office hours, ambulance facility may be requested from caretakers of the hostel. The request time and other details have to be entered in the register kept for this purpose for quality check and improvement. This vehicle is available only for emergency purposes, and not for scheduled doctor visits or for visiting diagnostic centers. (<a href="ambulance.php">Click here for Guidelines</a>)
</p>
<p align="justify">
<b>(2) 108 Service:</b> In case, the Institute ambulance is not available or being used by someone else, you may call 108.

</p>
<p align="justify">
<b>(3) Nearby Hospitals:</b> We also have signed MoU with two nearby hospitals, whose ambulance can be availed free of cost.<br/> 
<ul>
	
<li>Continental Hospital (Emergency: 040 6700 0111)</li><br/>
<li>Himagiri Hospital (Emergency: 040 2300 4206)</li>
</ul>
</p>
